            <note>The division into chapters is taken from
               the edition <bibl><ptr target="bm:Platonov2002Lies"/></bibl>.</note>      
            
          <div type="edition">
                  <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="1" xml:id="PartOne">
                     <label>Part 1</label>
                     <ab>እኔ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ በጽድቅ፡ ጸራኁህ፡ እጅኽንም፡ ያዝሁኽ፡ 
                        ጠበቅሁኽም፡ ለሕዝብም፡ ኪዳን፡ አደረግሁኽ፡ ለአሕዛብም፡ ብርሃን።</ab>                     
                  </div>
             
             <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="2" xml:id="PartTwo">
                <label>Part 2</label>
                     <ab>ሙሴ፡ ሌዤአን፡ ሞንሰኘር፡ ደዢቆብ፡ የሚነቅፉበት፡</ab>                     
                  </div>
                  </div>
             
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="3" xml:id="PartThree">
               <label>Part 3</label>
                     <ab>በ፭ኛው፡ አኃዝ፡ እንዳየነ፡ ሙሴ፡ ሌዢአን፡ ሞንሰኘር፡ ደዢቆብ፡ ወደ፡ ምስር፡ መመለሳቸው፡ ነቅፈዋል።</ab>    
                  </div>
            
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="4" xml:id="PartFour">
               <label>Part 4</label>
                <ab>ሞንሰኘር፡ ደዢቆብ፡ ት፡ ፲፭ዓመት፡ ያህል፡ በትግሬ፡ ከኖሩ፡ በኋላ፡</ab>    
                  </div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="5" xml:id="PartFive">
               <label>Part 5</label>
                <ab>ታሪከ፡ ነገሥት፡ እንዳለ፡</ab>    
                  </div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter" n="6" xml:id="PartSix">
               <label>Part 6</label>
                     <ab>ከዚህ፡ በፊት፡ እንዳልኍ፡ ራስ፡ ኃይሉና፡ ታላቁ፡ ራስ፡ ዓሊ፡</ab>
                  </div>
            <div type="textpart" subtype="colophon" n="7" xml:id="Colophon">
               <label>Colophon</label>
               <ab>አነ፡ ካህን፡ <persName ref="PRS12520TaklaH">ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡</persName> ወልዱ፡ ለካህን፡ ተክለ፡ እግዚእ፡</ab>
            </div>
